# Keep text files LF in the working tree on every platform. Without this, the
# Windows CI runner (core.autocrlf=true) checks the committed LF header out as
# CRLF, while cbindgen regenerates LF — so the header-freshness gate mismatches.
* text=auto eol=lf

*.png binary
*.dll binary
*.lib binary
*.pdb binary
*.exp binary
